<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79c5be34-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s3774"><num value="3774">§ 3774.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated to carry out this chapter not more than $75,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2025 through 2029.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id79c5be35-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/294/s5">Pub. L. 109–294, § 5</ref>, <date date="2006-10-03">Oct. 3, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/1354">120 Stat. 1354</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/116/9/tVII/s7001/a">Pub. L. 116–9, title VII, § 7001(a)</ref>, <date date="2019-03-12">Mar. 12, 2019</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/133/779">133 Stat. 779</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/118/159/dE/tLIII/s5302">Pub. L. 118–159, div. E, title LIII, § 5302</ref>, <date date="2024-12-23">Dec. 23, 2024</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/138/2445">138 Stat. 2445</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
